{"tid":2239767,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何栢良復出分析疫情","createTime":"2020-10-12T08:10:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T08:51:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"672419d08392900f06edef3df779f29190fe9bc2","tid":2239767,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T08:10:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201012/K5CYUHAZ4REILDHNW5WMD2MX2Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201012%2FK5CYUHAZ4REILDHNW5WMD2MX2Y%2F&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBUigq9hDTRyGE5nekVWm24Q%3D&h=9c914ba7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201012%2FK5CYUHAZ4REILDHNW5WMD2MX2Y%2F&h=623d9934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201012/K5CYUHAZ4REILDHNW5WMD2MX2Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n何栢良復出分析疫情<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/D_CUvV7xLFFTva3vXcamyORB6j4=/1578x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AILPBNL3QFGPDIWCFSTWJVZYGE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FD_CUvV7xLFFTva3vXcamyORB6j4%3D%2F1578x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAILPBNL3QFGPDIWCFSTWJVZYGE.jpg&h=27117f37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■何栢良今接受港台節目訪問評疫情。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今年初武漢肺炎爆發後，幾乎每日接受電台訪問分析疫情的港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：酒客「交換口水」或步紐約後塵20%人感染  袁國勇：冬季疫潮恐殺千人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被林鄭轟「所謂專家」<br />\n<br />\n林鄭政府為配合內地支援香港抗疫，漠視民意上月強推全民檢測，多名專家質疑檢測成效之餘，更表態不參與計劃。何栢良當時表示因生活繁忙及對成效有疑問，加上他嚴格管理生活，感染機會微乎其微，故不會檢測。林鄭之後批評「所謂專家、醫生和一些人抹黑計劃」，阻止市民檢測，出於政治計算抹黑中央。<br />\n<br />\n何栢良8月26日透過短訊向商台表示暫停每日在商台訪問環節，呼籲「市民大眾要平心靜氣，用科學原則去應對，疫境自強」。當時《晴朗》主持人估計在林鄭「出咗聲」的政治氣氛下，專家們承受壓力，難暢所欲言。惟事隔逾月，本港疫情反彈，何栢良決定今日復出，在早上9時15分的《千禧年代》訪問中再為公眾分析疫情，為本港防疫工作出力。"},{"pid":"82e9740bdf4601e3f58e6afc0e2252f589d6373b","tid":2239767,"uid":50894,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T08:12:44.000Z","msg":"未來14日是關鍵"},{"pid":"77c3d9d2b44add4dd84fb9deaeba6c30e326c723","tid":2239767,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T08:14:47.000Z","msg":"恐懼撚進場<br />\n配合政府搞禁聚令"},{"pid":"f46c4ddeaee057c8e2d74d99cb6109ca6ce46ef1","tid":2239767,"uid":49329,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T08:17:15.000Z","msg":"用科學原則去應對，疫境自強！<br />\n<br />\n何醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1642621e981e50077852ed619b3f683c5d4bff4","tid":2239767,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T08:17:56.000Z","msg":"佢正一9up多過呼吸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99909c038692bce9e1f9ab56f1d9b6916f6a6e99","tid":2239767,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"82e9740bdf4601e3f58e6afc0e2252f589d6373b","tid":2239767,"uid":50894,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T08:12:44.000Z","msg":"未來14日是關鍵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T08:18:39.000Z","msg":"back seat driver 何帕文"},{"pid":"edf1494bb5b0d5d4cea917235cb1d461b99841c3","tid":2239767,"uid":210280,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T08:20:37.000Z","msg":"過街老鼠"},{"pid":"98600e10b5054d0b65d47314e7faf0bfb5978920","tid":2239767,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T08:26:49.000Z","msg":"小心d都好嘅, 自己就話身體強壯啫, 但傳咗俾老一輩就唔一定冇事喎!"},{"pid":"028090ef9974d17705123f6597e1aa766ee7dfa6","tid":2239767,"uid":35924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"77c3d9d2b44add4dd84fb9deaeba6c30e326c723","tid":2239767,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T08:1